An example IMPACT cBioPortal mutation data set in API format

Source: R/data.R
sv.Rd

This set was created from a random sample of 200 patients from publicly available prostate cancer data from cBioPortal. The file is in API format.

sv

Format

A data frame with structural variants from Abida et al. JCO Precis Oncol 2017. Retrieved from cBioPortal.There are 94 observations and 29 variables.

A data frame with 94 rows and 44 variables:
